2. Malosi           [scintillation]<br>
3. Char             [Sirroco][Rain of Swords]{Lvl 1 DD}<br>
4. Scars of sigil   [Shock/Char]<br>
5. Call of the Hero [Gate]<br>
6. Summonings       [Self Buffs]<br>
7. Burnout III      [Renew Summoning]<br>
8. Cadeau of Flame  [Renew elements] {Invis while traveling}<br>
<br>
I don't always have gate up.. While traveling I always have it up, and soloing mid lvl dungeons... When soloing outdoors I now prefer CoH as I dont have to zone, Just out run mobs and CoH.. and I pull with either malosi or Annul magic.. depends if they are a caster.  <br>
<br>
I ALWAYS have Annul Magic up. Incase I find that roaming shaman with SoW on while traveling and invis happens to fail.<br>
<br>
Mid level dungeons are done by parking pet in a previously cleared area and pulling with lvl 1 DD burst of flame.<br>
Pet and DS do all the work, and only in freak occurances i have to nuke with Char which would be in slot 4.<br>
<br>
Renew elements only in slot 8 after I DS pet and am ready to pull while [soloing]...  Slot 7 Renew summoning... Is memmed while [soloing] and I refresh BOIII here as it presents itself.   I prefer to heal more and let DS do it's job and only nuke a couple times... more mana efficient IMO.<br>
<br>
6 is used for summonings and to refresh buffs ALWAYS.<br>
<br>
I also arrange my spellbook so spells that share a slot are close together for easy memming during battle. not giving the exact order... (my little secret}<br>
<br>
Spellbook is arranged high lvl spells from page 1-5 usefull summonings 6-10... old spells are stored in back of spellbook... out of sight out of mind.<br>
This makes entering the game and going to spellbook for spell transition fluid. and I dont have to change pages often. Same applies for easy of transition during battle.<br>
<br>
Scintillation in slot 2 for AoE raids..<br>
Scirroco in slot 3 for soloing out doors.<br>
Scars of sigil is used for soloing in tandem with scirroco unless I'm soloing FR mobs ex. Skyfire.. then I use shock and Rain of Swords till I can Mem Manastorm.<br>
<br>
Pet is almost always memmed in slot 6 until I need to buff/conjure etc.  and only in rare occurences do I use Rage of Zomm in this slot.<br>
<br>
Char is used with SoSigil in group combat.. soon to be 57 Shock.<br>
<br>
Developed this over the years. very efficient and allows me to use new spells in same scheme as I can scribe them.<br>
<br>
I challenge anyone to find a faster quicker more efficient system.<br>
<br>
Belthezzar Magius 56 c0njur3r of Mithaniel Marr<br>
Majick Le'Deliciou 46 Ench<br>
Phatty Lumpkin 34 cleric<br>
Solemn 15 Shadow Knight<br>
<br>
Mithaniel Marr server<br>
<br>
2 year veteran and lvl 50 8 months before Kunark came out...<br>
