<br>
Cinder Bolt: good spell all around if you can keep the dang tanks from standing in your way.My wife plays a Pally, only tank I can get to understand that direct spells dont hit if you stand in the way.<br>
<br>
Blaze: Just in case the tank you are with is a complete moron and does not understand<br>
<br>
Rain Of Spikes: well if you have more than one mob stand back and let them have it...<br>
<br>
Malise:What can I say...awesome spell. I use it personally cause I have seen significant increase in my wife's root ability. Yes she does seem to root better than the earth pet.<br>
<br>
Inferno Shield: Pally lives mage lives...nuff said<br>
<br>
Renew Summoning: Yes even the best pet needs a little health now and then...I have actually lived thru a fight with a red by just chain casting this spell on him.<br>
<br>
Gate: If in doubt...GATE OUT<br>
<br>
