2. Elemental Maelstrom<br>
3. Shock of whatever the heck it is 595 damage conj.<br>
4. pet / blaze <br>
5. BO II<br>
6. Renew Elements/See Invis/Summon Crap<br>
7. Damage Shield<br>
8. Gate<br>
<br>
I've always wondered what exactly makes people pick the order of their spells.  Malisement is almost always the first spell I cast on a mob solo or grouped unless they have a ds...  Then I usually cast either Elemental Maelstrom or Shock... then let things go and maybe help out or not.  I put gate at the bottom because it seems to be the closest to click on then... damn not having any other escape spells.<br>
 Anuire The Drunken Mage<br>
