2 - Shock of Swords<br>
3 - pet heal (or sometimes group dmg shield or Malosi)<br>
4 - BO3<br>
5 - Dmg Shield<br>
6 - Malisement<br>
7 - gate<br>
8 - pet (use this space for temporarily memming buffs)<br>
<br>
I just don't get why anyone would keep a buff memorized.  IMHO, you should keep memmed the spells you might need in combat.  When a buff drops, swap it out temporarily with the pet summon, buff yourself, then remem pet.  Nice to have that pet spell memmed in the case of a bad pull where you might have to chain cast, and you don't want to have to sit down to mem it during a fight, as you'll likely get jumped on.<br>
 <p>Nybbik Fyzlfop<br>
53 Elementalist<br>
Reckoning of Honor<br>
